name: Why Is The Sky Blue V2

metadata.name: Hut of Empyrean
metadata.description:
Don't be afraid to ask stupid questions and look at things from a different angle. You'll find where is the hut of Empyrean.

About the collection:  
BLUES collects moments of the purity of the sky through the prism of an undying interest in the surrounding reality. These are different facets of one state of desire to see something new and lightful in this world again. Why Is The Sky Blue is the quintessence of purity balance of openness to the world and finding oneself in it.
